## Quality Dimensions

Rate each 1-5 every 5 loops. Score below 4 = generate task targeting the gap.

| Dimension | Score | Biggest Gap | Last Assessed |
|-----------|-------|-------------|---------------|
| Correctness | ?/5 | (What breaks or could break?) | — |
| Test Coverage | ?/5 | (What is untested?) | — |
| Security | ?/5 | (What is exposed?) | — |
| Performance | ?/5 | (What is slow?) | — |
| UX / Usability | ?/5 | (What confuses users?) | — |
| Code Quality | ?/5 | (What is tangled or fragile?) | — |
| Documentation | ?/5 | (What is undocumented?) | — |
| Resilience | ?/5 | (What fails ungracefully?) | — |

Scoring: 1=broken, 2=minimal, 3=adequate, 4=solid, 5=excellent.
**Score 5 requires evidence** (test result, audit report, metric). No evidence = at most 4.

